  m_Name: GSWGA_Course_3_Lesson_3_Q4
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::QuestionData
  question: "Which prompting technique best matches the given scenario?\nA team requests
    the LLM to \u201CProduce an analysis encapsulating the nuanced aspects of this
    topic\u201D, but the output is overly broad and misses key points."
  answers:
  - Define the task clearly
  - Be specific
  - Include examples
  - Use simple and direct language
  maxSelections: 1
  correctAnswerIndices: 03000000
  correctMessage: "Using clear, direct instructions such as \u201CWrite a 200-word
    summary of the article\u2019s main points\u201D minimizes ambiguity and improves
    the response."
  incorrectMessage: "Not quite. Consider how simplifying and clarifying instructions
    can improve the quality of the LLM\u2019s output."
